It's me...

247
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,682
I said it's me!!

248
00:18:16,707 --> 00:18:18,234
Mom!

249
00:18:18,719 --> 00:18:22,741
It's me, Mom...

250
00:18:33,279 --> 00:18:36,169
That kiddo...

251
00:18:36,273 --> 00:18:40,843
liked potato salad so much.

252
00:18:42,673 --> 00:18:45,073
Mom...

253
00:18:54,688 --> 00:18:57,918
Then, she was helped by my sister,

254
00:18:57,943 --> 00:19:04,010
and they made
potato salad for me.

255
00:19:28,256 --> 00:19:30,136
So...

256
00:19:30,379 --> 00:19:31,865
How is it?

257
00:19:32,684 --> 00:19:35,591
That rascal liked it so much,

258
00:19:35,803 --> 00:19:39,603
he would keep asking for more.

259
00:19:42,443 --> 00:19:45,443
He's so affectionate...

260
00:19:47,079 --> 00:19:51,669
and caring, such a good boy.

261
00:19:57,336 --> 00:19:59,330
But it was...

262
00:20:00,616 --> 00:20:02,256
so salty.

263
00:20:03,130 --> 00:20:05,080
So damn salty.

264
00:20:09,130 --> 00:20:11,460
Master...

265
00:20:14,791 --> 00:20:16,884
Accept...

266
00:20:17,656 --> 00:20:20,126
my apologies.

267
00:20:26,089 --> 00:20:28,576
Thanks to you...

268
00:20:29,710 --> 00:20:32,474
Thanks to what you told me...

269
00:20:35,029 --> 00:20:39,368
I was able to see my mother.

270
00:20:43,809 --> 00:20:45,849
I apologize!

271
00:20:46,973 --> 00:20:50,183
I'm sorry...

272
00:20:52,795 --> 00:20:55,295
What are you saying?

273
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:57,810
I'm sorry...

274
00:20:58,041 --> 00:21:00,431
Stop saying that!

275
00:21:00,829 --> 00:21:03,159
Isn't that all the better?

276
00:21:07,132 --> 00:21:10,636
Go visit her often.

277
00:21:12,730 --> 00:21:14,880
Yes.

278
00:21:23,152 --> 00:21:24,722
Here.

279
00:21:25,753 --> 00:21:28,353
On the house.

280
00:21:31,073 --> 00:21:33,043
Thank you.

281
00:22:00,046 --> 00:22:01,786
So good...

282
00:22:07,779 --> 00:22:10,239
Reminds me of home.

283
00:22:15,482 --> 00:22:17,275
Maybe I'm getting old?

284
00:22:17,508 --> 00:22:18,754
But, these days...

285
00:22:18,779 --> 00:22:21,849
I seem to cry for the smallest things.

286
00:22:26,519 --> 00:22:30,892
~ to be continued ~

287
00:22:31,312 --> 00:22:36,069
And here's your one
point advice for potato salad.

288
00:22:36,645 --> 00:22:40,551
<i>Boil the potatoes without peeling them,</i>

289
00:22:40,603 --> 00:22:42,543
<i>and you'll maintain their unique taste.</i>

290
00:22:43,533 --> 00:22:46,823
If you add the onions
while the potatoes are still hot,

291
00:22:47,089 --> 00:22:49,979
they'll become soft and tasty.

292
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:59,640
<i>Let's add mayo when
the potatoes have cooled down.</i>

293
00:23:02,196 --> 00:23:05,026
<i>So that's the secret
behind a proper potato salad.</i>

294
00:23:05,655 --> 00:23:07,025
And so here we are...

295
00:23:07,770 --> 00:23:09,100
Good night everyone.

